{"tid":1805371,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"1月1日 14:00 民陣元旦大遊行   毋忘承諾，並肩同行，五大訴求，缺一不可","createTime":"2019-12-31T15:11:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-01T03:53:33.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c23b747dd36d9550de3fc7482d6ddd138d0182fa","tid":1805371,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T15:11:23.000Z","msg":"1月1日 14:00 民陣元旦大遊行   <br />\n毋忘承諾，並肩同行，五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2695522603828447&amp;id=511608535553209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2695522603828447%26id%3D511608535553209&d=WJuKoENqNSNgO%2FFXDb0as5mjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=8e85616d\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2695522603828447&amp;id=511608535553209</a><br />\n<br />\n【元旦大遊行 不反已出】<br />\n<br />\n民陣已收到警方發出的不反對通知書，<br />\n可以正式同各位講多次，1.1 維園見！<br />\n<br />\n元旦遊行當日將會有超過 40 個新成立工會同大家見面，歡迎大家了解詳情，加入你所屬行業的工會，壯大抗爭的組織力量。<br />\n<br />\n毋忘承諾，並肩同行，五大訴求，缺一不可，<br />\n一月一，維園見！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">【民陣元旦大遊行】<br />\n2020.1.1 星期三 Wednesday｜2PM<br />\n維園中央草坪 遊行至 遮打道行人專用區<br />\nFrom Victoria Park (Central Lawn) to <br />\nChater Road Pedestrian Precinct</span><br />\n<br />\n*已取得不反對通知書<br />\n*Letter of No Objection Received<br />\n<br />\n【海報、單張下載】 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2QwFg31\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2QwFg31&d=WJuKoENqNSNgO%2FFXDb0as5mjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=731d05f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2QwFg31</a><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n【民陣 TG】 <a href=\"http://t.me/CivilHumanRightsFront\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FCivilHumanRightsFront&d=WJuKoENqNSNgO%2FFXDb0as5mjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=656a033a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/CivilHumanRightsFront</a><br />\n【民陣 Twitter】 <a href=\"http://twitter.com/chrf_hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lih